OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA warm end
OL,6,Fto the day with some late evening
OL,7,Fsunshine. Staying dry overnight with
OL,8,Fvariable cloud around throughout.
OL,9,FTemperatures dipping lower than of
OL,10,Flate, feeling cool in rural spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FAnother dry and bright day
OL,13,Fahead with plenty of sunshine, Light
OL,14,Fnortherly winds and feeling warm once
OL,15,Fagain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
